I agree with you totally, Juli.  I admit that I used to give upwards of 25 seconds between questions.  I&#39;ve learned that if I&#39;m going to get an answer, it usually comes a lot sooner than that, if not, then I&#39;m not getting an answer at that time.  But that had to come with learning.  

Jeremy



----- Original Message ----
From: juli velazquez &lt;ghostchasingfool@...&gt;
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
